---
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-[#1A1A1A] text-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 text-[#F4A261]">
        <span class="lang-ar">رؤى المراجعات النصية</span>
        <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">Review Insights</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed opacity-90 mb-6 border-l-0 rtl:border-r-4 ltr:border-l-4 border-[#F4A261]/40 pl-0 rtl:pr-6 ltr:pl-6">
        <span class="lang-ar">
          تكشف المراجعات النصية للزوار ما يقدره الضيوف فعلاً.
        </span>
        <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">
          Written customer reviews provide insight into what visitors actually value.
        </span>
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-70">
        <span class="lang-ar">
          فعلى عكس التقييمات الرقمية (النجوم الخمسة)، توضح التعليقات المكتوبة تفاصيل التجربة الحقيقية للزبائن كجودة الطعام، دفء الضيافة، والأجواء الاجتماعية.
        </span>
        <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">
          Unlike star ratings, review text reveals priorities such as food quality, hospitality, atmosphere, and social experience.
        </span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stylized Quote / Focus block -->
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#F4A261]/10 to-transparent blur-xl rounded-full"></div>
      <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm relative">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-12 h-12 text-[#F4A261]/40 mb-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
        <blockquote class="text-2xl font-bold leading-tight uppercase tracking-wider opacity-90 italic">
          <span class="lang-ar">"النجوم تقيس الرضا، بينما الكلمات تقيس التجربة."</span>
          <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">"Stars measure satisfaction, but words measure the experience."</span>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
